****************************************Ansilounge*****************************************************
PLEASE NOTE: Install script is designed for CentOS systems. If you want to use a different OS, please
do a manual installation.

Before you execute the install script, please do the following:

yum -y install git

git clone https://bitbucket.org/globaldyne/ansilounge-prod.git

create a mysql user ansilounge with the same password and give full permission to ansilounge db

CREATE USER 'ansilounge'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'ansilounge';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON * . * TO 'ansilounge'@'localhost';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

